blktap (2.0.90-2ubuntu4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Enable HA by default

    Introduce new option 'enable-ha'. High availability
    is enabled by default (on).

    Usage: openvstorage+[tcp|rdma]:ip:port/volume,enable-ha=[on|off]

